item.title: Belgium
item.description: Europe Part 3 - Belgium # Brussels # I was only in Belgium for one night, but I had a lot of fun. I stayed in Brussels. It’s a beautiful city, of course. Birthplace of Audrey Hepburn, location of an escape room I nearly had a chance to try and escape except for the drunk northern irish couple who puked everywhere and offered me 50 euros to ‘settle it’.
